#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><h3>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:22
#, fuzzy
msgid "AWS"
msgstr "AWS"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:23
#, fuzzy
msgid "AWS aids Quarkus by donating credits, enabling developers to use AWS services for testing, CI, and feature development. This support accelerates Quarkus innovation, enhancing the cloud-native experience on AWS."
msgstr "AWS 通过捐赠代金券支持 Quarkus，使开发者能够使用 AWS 服务进行测试、持续集成（CI）和功能开发。这一支持加速了 Quarkus 的创新，提升了在 AWS 上的云原生体验。"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:24
#, fuzzy
msgid "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/opensource/\" target=\"blank\">Learn more about open source at AWS</a>"
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/opensource/\" target=\"blank\">在 AWS 上深入了解开源</a>"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><h3>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:27
#, fuzzy
msgid "GitHub"
msgstr "GitHub"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:28
#, fuzzy
msgid "GitHub's donation of GitHub Actions runners aids the Quarkus team by providing dedicated compute resources. This contribution eases infrastructure strain, accelerates development and testing, and boosts community collaboration."
msgstr "GitHub 捐赠的 GitHub Actions 运行器通过提供专用的计算资源，为 Quarkus 团队提供了支持。这一贡献缓解了基础设施的压力，加快了开发和测试进程，并促进了社区协作。"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:29
#, fuzzy
msgid "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/actions/concepts/runners/github-hosted-runners\" target=\"blank\">Learn more about GitHub Action runners</a>"
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/actions/concepts/runners/github-hosted-runners\" target=\"blank\">了解有关 GitHub Action 运行器的更多信息</a>"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><h3>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:32
#, fuzzy
msgid "Gradle Technologies"
msgstr "Gradle Technologies"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:33
#, fuzzy
msgid "Gradle Technologies significantly supports the Quarkus ecosystem by donating a Develocity instance. This donation offers Quarkus developers advanced build insights and performance analytics, optimizing build processes for faster debugging, improved reliability, and enhanced productivity."
msgstr "Gradle Technologies 通过捐赠一个 Develocity 实例，为 Quarkus 生态系统提供了有力支持。此次捐赠为 Quarkus 开发者提供了先进的构建洞察和性能分析功能，通过优化构建流程，从而加快调试速度、提高可靠性并提升生产力。"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:34
#, fuzzy
msgid "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://gradle.com/develocity/\" target=\"blank\">Learn more about Develocity</a>"
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://gradle.com/develocity/\" target=\"blank\">了解有关 Develocity 的更多信息</a>"

