#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><h3>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:42
#, fuzzy
msgid "IBM"
msgstr "IBM"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:43
#, fuzzy
msgid "IBM strengthened its Java and Quarkus commitment by moving the Red Hat engineers working on Quarkus into IBM. This ensured dedicated resources for Quarkus's growth, deepening IBM's open-source involvement and focus on cloud-native Java for enterprises."
msgstr "IBM 通过将负责 Quarkus 开发的红帽工程师调入 IBM，进一步强化了其对 Java 和 Quarkus 的承诺。此举确保了 Quarkus 发展所需的专项资源，深化了 IBM 在开源领域的参与，并强化了其对企业级云原生 Java 的关注。"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:44
#, fuzzy
msgid "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://www.ibm.com/opensource/\" target=\"blank\">Learn more about open source at IBM</a>"
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://www.ibm.com/opensource/\" target=\"blank\">了解有关 IBM 开源项目的更多信息</a>"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><h3>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:47
#, fuzzy
msgid "Red Hat"
msgstr "红帽"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:48
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus originated at Red Hat, which ensured its ongoing development and stability by employing many of its principal engineers. This support helped cultivate a strong ecosystem for cloud-native application development. A key reason for Quarkus's transition to the Commonhaus Foundation was Red Hat's dedication to its open-source nature."
msgstr "Quarkus 起源于红帽（Red Hat），该公司通过聘用其众多核心工程师，确保了该项目的持续开发和稳定性。这种支持有助于培育一个强大的云原生应用开发生态系统。Quarkus 转由 Commonhaus 基金会接管的一个关键原因，是红帽对其开源性质的坚定承诺。"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:49
#, fuzzy
msgid "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://www.redhat.com/en/blog/what-does-open-source-program-office-do\" target=\"blank\">Learn more about open source at Red Hat</a>"
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://www.redhat.com/en/blog/what-does-open-source-program-office-do\" target=\"blank\">在红帽深入了解开源</a>"

